sect1.para:
Sink elements can derive from GstBaseSink using
the usual GObject type creation voodoo, or by
using the convenience macro GST_BOILERPLATE ():

sect1.programlisting:
GST_BOILERPLATE_FULL (GstMySink, gst_my_sink, GstBaseSink, GST_TYPE_BASE_SINK);

